result.title: Practice contest + goodbye!
result.content:
Hi everyone! The practice contest for matchings and network flows is now up in the group. It is open indefinitely, so you can just solve problems at your leisure.

I had a great time with you this week! If you still have questions about anything, you can PM me here or in Telegram (the nickname is that same as here), I will try my best to answer, at least for the duration of the camp. Hope to see all of you soon!
